headline: Why The Trade Desk (TTD) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of digital advertising platform The Trade Desk (NASDAQ:TTD) jumped 4.3% in the afternoon session after an analyst note eased investor concerns about its relationship with a key client, Walmart.
